I really enjoyed the concept of Doodle Creatures. It's a pretty fun puzzle game which isn't too taxing, most of the combinations are easy to find. With the original 1000 credits you only need to spend them on disabling repetition which makes the game even easier. The three puzzles on offer are over-simplistic. While this is a fairly fun game, compared to the other games in the serious, it's far too easy with little to offer after completion.
